data.description: Rare opportunity to own this sprawling 41-acre homestead equipped with a barn, and 4 run-ins for horses.  Upon entering the home, you will notice the large rocking-chair front porch where great memories of spending time with family and friends can be made.  There is NO carpet in this lovely ranch home - only engineered hardwood flooring and ceramic tile. The living area is very spacious and has a charming gas (propane tank) stone fireplace which will be perfect for hanging your Christmas stocking on. Enjoy cooking and serving meals in the large eat-in kitchen - all kitchen appliances convey with the sale. It will be easy to unwind each day in the primary bedroom which offers sizable living space, a new walk-in shower, and a walk-in closet.  There are two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom down the hall and the 4th bedroom, which could also be used as an office or flex space, is right off the eat-in kitchen. The laundry room has an exit door that will take you to the covered patio where you can enjoy barbequing rain or shine. Recent upgrades include the installation of premium insulated siding (2020), new well tank and motor/pump (2022) and the metal roof is only 8 years old.  The barn is equipped with electricity, water lines and has plenty of space to store your farm equipment and hay.  The storage shed does not have electricity but does convey with the sale.  This property is perfect for livestock with 4 run-ins for horses and a fenced-in round pen.  The deer stand will make it easy to hunt deer on your 41 acres.  On hot summer days, you can cool off by taking a dip in the above ground pool.  This is a great home, in a great location and USDA 100% financing is available to qualified buyers.  Schedule an appointment today to check out this property!
